 
<p>
Republicans changed their mind about veterans poisoned by military
incineration of toxic substances, and 
<a href="https://www.theguardian.com/us-news/2022/aug/03/senate-passes-pact-act-veterans-toxins-burn-pits">passed a bill to help them.</a>
<p>
They tried following their philosophy, which is that if you're not
rich you don't deserve help, but the public disgust made them change
their tune.

 